snippet.title: Trace Hunters | Steam Next Fest Dev Stream VOD
snippet.description:
Trace Hunters was in Steam's June Next Fest! 

Trace Hunters is a third-person shooter where you pilot a futuristic combat vehicle and fend off a horde of robots. This is my stream video of me playing through the first two levels of the game, as well as showing off some weapons not included in the demo.

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2706210?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=nextfeststream
